  "title": "Community Development & Engagement Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Plan and deliver family development programmes that foster positive values and promote resilient families anchored on Islamic faith and identity, ensuring effective implementation and stakeholder engagement. Lead volunteer management initiatives that sustain volunteer motivation and contributions to the Mosque</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Design and execute targeted programmes to cultivate positive values and strengthen family resilience based on Islamic principles</li><li>Manage end-to-end implementation of Family Development programmes, including administration and payment processing to ensure smooth operations</li><li>Collaborate with internal departments, key stakeholders, and external partners to coordinate and optimize programme delivery</li><li>Build and maintain trusting relationships with families and stakeholders to provide comprehensive support tailored to their needs</li><li>Lead volunteer management by developing outreach and engagement strategies that sustain volunteer motivation and contributions to the Mosque</li><li>Conduct annual programme evaluations to identify improvements and develop actionable plans and budgets for the department</li><li>Support the Head of Community Outreach and Management by performing additional duties as assigned</li></ul>",
